wikipedia_page.main: Eloise Jayne "Ellie" Wilson (born 11 May 1997) is an English footballer who plays as a defender for FA Women's Championship club Sheffield United. She previously played for Reading F.C. and London Bees. She has represented England on the under-19 and under-23 national teams.
